<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169904>
    bibo:endPage "47" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "37" ;
    bibo:volume "1046" ;
    dc:creator "Pinho, Luiz Carlos De; Mendes, Humberto Fonseca; Marcondes, Carlos Brisola" ;
    dc:date "2005" ;
    dc:title "A new Brazilian species of Stenochironomus Kieffer mining decayed leaves in bromeliads (Diptera: Chironomidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169905>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169906>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169907>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169908> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169905>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Stenochironomus atlanticus Pinho & Mendes new species, male imago. A, head. B, cibarial pump, tentorium, and stipes. C, thorax. D, wing. E, anal point and tergite IX and dorsal aspect of left gonocoxite and gonostylus. F, hypopygium with anal point and tergite IX removed, left dorsal aspect, right ventral aspect." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169905/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169906>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Stenochironomus atlanticus Pinho & Mendes new species, female imago. A, genitalia, dorsal view. B, genitalia, ventral view. C, dorsomesal lobe. D, apodeme lobe of gonapophysis VIII. E, ventrolateral lobe of gonapophysis IX." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169907>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Stenochironomus atlanticus Pinho & Mendes new species, pupa. A, frontal apotome. B, basal ring of thoracic horn and precorneals. C, thorax. D, tergites I – V. E, tergites VI – IX." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169907/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169908>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Stenochironomus atlanticus Pinho & Mendes new species, larva. A, head capsule, dorsal aspect. B, head capsule, ventral aspect. C, antenna. D, labrum. E, mandible. F, mentum and paralabial plate. G, labiohypopharynx. H, anal end." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169908/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

